So we were curious about what the extra passages would be like where the main character gets out of his car and does whatever he wants.
As is already the case in the NFS series, the result is completely different from what was expected.
These are potentially arcade racing games but the whole thing is going down because of some unnecessary bugs that have been around for several years.
