The result is that this element is not likely to interfere and, in the context described above, is one of the elements that enhance the game.
The driving pattern is in the tradition of the previous games.
Which means that there's nothing extraordinary about it right now, but you can't say it's negative.
As for the realistic simulation, you'll have to look elsewhere.
But while we can find better in the competition the driving model goes very well with the type of race design.
So it's all right.
