Park or mountain?
The architects agree on the appropriateness of the summons beyond the controversy over fees
The municipal contest on the 16 doors reopens the debate on the role of Collserola in Barcelona
In the mid-1980s, at the height of the now-defunct Barcelona Metropolitan Corporation (CMB), the administration printed posters promoting Collserola.
