The competition, both in terms of its organisation and in terms of reflecting on the city, is a topic of conversation for all the architects in Barcelona.
It's almost a recurring theme that two members of this ancient caste of elected officials speak of when they recognize each other in an elevator.
And this is one of the few opinions on which three architects from Barcelona, university professors, who presented themselves, agree.
Miguel Roldn, Daniel Modol and Marta Bayona: the competition is timely.
For Roldn, after approaching the coastal front "it is necessary" to debate "the mountain front" because the speech of Ildefons Cerda, that of the green houses blocks was not carried out.
"We must start from the premise that the largest park in Barcelona is the beach.
Among other things, it is very accessible.
