For a typist from Sijn de Cali, the recognition that President Juan Manuel Santos gave to Eliazar Gonzlez, in a press conference for the operation against "Cano", is very significant.
A lot of people don't know what we do.
Fingerprinting is an exact science, with no margin for error, that can be crucial in solving crimes.
In addition to identifying the bodies, fingerprinting assisted in the investigation of crimes such as theft and murder and confirmed the identity of the persons captured.
When caught, many criminals present false identity cards or do not have any documents.
We're taking their fingerprints and running them through the database.
The investigator related that in one case of theft he had to remove a portion of a house's wall, since in this spot the thief had reached for his hand to pull out a safe full of jewelry and money.
"The walls are difficult because they are not adequate surfaces to take a fingerprint, but in this case we were able to get the fingerprint of the whole hand and identify the offender who had participated in various robberies", he recalls.
Fingerprints can also rule out or confirm suspects in homicide cases.
Recently, a man was found dead with bottles of liquor around him.
The investigation determined that a relative may be suspected of the crime and indeed a fingerprint on the bottle was a match.
Even though that doesn't guarantee he's the killer, it puts him at the scene of the crime.
A CTI fingerprint technician explained that "the fingerprints of objects are extracted with chemical or physical reagents".
When they appear, a pick-up line or a tape is used to pick them up.
Then the fingerprints are sent to Asif, the declinant database, or the National Civil Registry.
"The problem is that there are still many undocumented Colombians", said the ITC expert.
He explained that not everything is as it is shown on the CSI television program.
Not everything that glitters is gold, and not everything you touch is necessarily a print.
It can, however, be used, if the necessary confrontation is achieved.
